        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="flex-item-3col space-second">
      <hr class="mobile-hr yellow-hr">
      <div class="img-wrapper">
        <%=image_tag("birthday-cake-380178_640.jpg", :class => "img-responsive")%>
      </div>
      <div class="focusCopy">
        <h5><strong>2. DEDICATE A BIRTHDAY</strong></h5>
        <p>In lieu of gifts, ask for donations to be made in your name then pat yourself on the back. Your celebration just changed a life!
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="flex-item-3col space-second">
      <hr class="mobile-hr yellow-hr">
      <div class="img-wrapper">
        <%= image_tag("event_detroit.jpg", :class => "img-responsive")%>
      </div>
      <div class="focusCopy">
        <h5><strong>3. HOST AN EVENT</strong></h5>
        <p>Make a night of it! Invite friends and family over and let us join the fun! Host your book club, poker night, or wine party and collect donations toward a particular campus project or area of interest.
        </p>
      </div>
      <hr class="mobile-hr">
    </div>
  </div>
